## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4d8a2-151">Essa implementação do <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> pode ser útil em um aplicativo que deve chamar o `Fill` método para duas ou mais <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objetos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4d8a2-151">This implementation of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> can be useful in an application that must call the `Fill` method for two or more <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
